  "datePublished": "2026-03-06",
  "description": "A ***user guide*** is a document that teaches someone how to use a product, system, or service. It differs from a [tutorial](./tutorial.md) in scope: a tutorial walks the reader through one task to build a skill; a user guide covers the product comprehensively, organized so readers can find what they need when they need it.",
